    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This design considerations document is meant to present more detail than the working group charter.  Specifically, it presents the areas that the working group will investigate and consider while developing a protocol specification for NFS version 4.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
